<p>Coinmama got its start in Israel in 2013. Since then, the firm has grown a lot. It now helps over 3.1 million customers from 188 countries buy and sell cryptocurrency. The team at Coinmama is made up of more than 35 people who work hard to make things go smoothly.</p>



<p>With close to ten years in business, they are well known for being a trusted place to trade digital money like Bitcoin or Ethereum. They stand tall as one of the legit players in the crypto world today.</p>



