<h2 class="wp-block-heading">KuCoin Review: Pros and Cons</h2>



<p>KuCoin is a cryptocurrency exchange that has some pros and cons. One of the advantages of using KuCoin is that it offers low trading fees compared to other exchanges. This can save you money when you buy or sell cryptocurrencies.</p>



<p>Another positive aspect is that KuCoin has a supportive customer service team. They are usually able to help users with any issues they may have. However, there are also some downsides to using KuCoin.</p>



<p>It&#8217;s important to note that KuCoin is not licensed in the U.S., so if you are located there, you won&#8217;t be able to use this platform. Additionally, funds kept on the KuCoin platform are not insured, which means there is a risk of losing your money if something goes wrong.</p>



<p>It&#8217;s worth mentioning that in 2020, KuCoin experienced a major hacking incident, which highlights the importance of keeping your crypto assets secure on any exchange platform.</p>



