<h3 class="wp-block-heading">KuCoin Community Chain (KCC)</h3>



<p>The KuCoin Community Chain (KCC) is a blockchain platform designed to make transactions faster and easier. It aims to remove barriers and allow the smooth flow of value across the globe.</p>



