<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What is Uphold?</h3>



<p>Uphold is a tool for trade. You can buy, sell, or swap many things here. It lets you deal with cryptocurrencies and other assets. The company that runs Uphold is in the United States.</p>



<p>It shows all deals and holdings as they happen to keep things clear and safe. They do not use user funds in any way.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How Does Uphold Work?</h3>



<p>Uphold is a place to trade many things. You move money to your Uphold account from your bank or credit card. Then, you can buy and sell different things like cryptocurrencies and other assets.</p>



<p>Everything happens on the Uphold app or website. The fees are clear, and it&#8217;s safe to take out your money when you&#8217;re done.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Uphold Features</h2>



