<li>Complete the verification process by providing the required personal information.</li>



<li>Deposit funds into your Uphold account using various payment methods, such as bank transfer or cryptocurrency deposit.</li>



<li>Choose the cryptocurrency or fiat currency you want to trade.</li>



<li>Select the trading pair you wish to trade, such as BTC/USD or ETH/EUR.</li>



<li>Specify the amount you want to buy or sell and review the transaction details.</li>



<li>Confirm the trade and wait for it to be executed.</li>



<li>Monitor your trades in your Uphold account dashboard.</li>



<li>If you want to sell your crypto assets, you can withdraw funds from your Uphold account to your bank account or another digital wallet.</li>



