<li><strong>Fee transparency</strong>: Uphold removes commissions and fees for deposits, withdrawals, and trading, allowing users to trade more efficiently without worrying about hidden costs.</li>



<li><strong>Staking feature</strong>: Uphold has a staking feature that allows users to earn up to 25% on their holdings, providing an opportunity for passive income.</li>



<li><strong>Secure platform</strong>: Uphold is a secure cloud-based financial service platform that prioritizes the safety of its users&#8217; transactions and personal information.</li>



<li><strong>Cross-asset transactions</strong>: Uphold enables individuals to securely transact across various asset classes, including cryptocurrencies, precious metals, and fiat currencies.</li>
</ol>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Disadvantages of Uphold</h3>



<p>Uphold has a few disadvantages that you should be aware of:</p>



<ol>
