<li>Uphold offers a limited selection of cryptocurrencies and precious metals for trading, which may not meet all investors&#8217; needs.</li>



<li>Uphold lacks some advanced trading tools and features that are available on other platforms.</li>



<li>While Uphold aims to reduce transaction costs and fees associated with currency exchange, some users may still find the fees to be higher than expected.</li>



<li>Some experts and crypto traders have criticized Uphold for its limited asset classes and higher fees compared to other leading exchanges.</li>
</ol>



